  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model predicts absolute hemolysis index for a Class III VAD at Model Risk Level 5 operating at 2500–5000 RPM with physiological flow rates of 3–6 L/min. Intended use: regulatory submission support for pre-market approval of an implantable VAD. All 13 credibility factors evaluated; seven factors achieved below required levels and six flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ performed. Decision: Accepted with conditions documented in the decision record.",
