      "rationale": "OpenFOAM v8 used with version control; regression tests cover 45% of hemolysis-relevant code paths. Independent review not completed. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification demonstrated via method of manufactured solutions for all governing equation terms including hemolysis transport.",
      "rationale": "MMS applied to Navier-Stokes only; hemolysis transport equation not verified via MMS. Second-order spatial convergence confirmed for momentum but not scalar transport. Gap remains at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation on three systematically refined meshes; GCI < 5% for hemolysis index QoI; mesh independence demonstrated at operating envelope extremes.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement performed (6M, 12M, 24M cells); GCI = 8.3% for hemolysis index at peak RPM. Criterion not met at envelope extremes. Achieved level 3 against required 4."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
