      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency analysis mapping validation experiment input parameters to COU input parameters; non-equivalencies identified and their impact on predictive confidence quantified.",
      "rationale": "Epistemic gap at MRL 5. No formal equivalency mapping between FDA benchmark experiment parameters and intended VAD COU parameters. Blood analog fluid properties differ from in-vivo conditions without impact assessment. Achieved level 1."
